---
title: Herby-Honey Haloumi & Veggie Couscous with Roasted Almonds & Yoghurt
description: Whip up a haloumi and couscous extravaganza in four easy steps. Drizzle over some honey to coat the haloumi and toss the
couscous with some carrot and courgette and it will look and taste like you’ve been cooking for hours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6690997d1f97e9ac1c52b5c5-785ead11.jpeg
